Provides a collection of interfaces and classes that compose the Java Accessibility Utilities.

Provides a set of "lightweight" (all-Java language) components that, to the maximum degree possible, work the same on all platforms.

Provides user interface objects built according to the Basic look and feel.

    static void SwingEventMonitor.removeChangeListener​(ChangeListener l)
    Removes the specified listener so it no longer receives CHANGE events when they occur.
